11 for the presence of a biomarker. Biomarker testing includes but is not limited to single-analyte
12 tests, multi-plex panel tests, protein expression, and whole exome, whole genome, and whole
13 transcriptomesequencing.
14 III. "Clinical utility" means a biomarker test result that provides information used in the
15 formulation of a treatment or monitoring strategy that informs a covered person's outcomes and
